body:
Changes the textures and names of the ZIRNOX Nuclear Reactor and its fuel rods to be more Beer-themed, every fuel rod is now based off of a type of alcoholic beverage.

- Natural Uranium = "Farmer Henry's" NU Pale-Lager;
- Uranium Fuel = "Caramel Dreams" Uranium Dutch Pale-Lager;
- Thorium-232 = Thorium Wash;
- Thorium Fuel = "Pantrybrew" Thoric Moonshine;
- MOX Fuel = "World's Crispest" MOX Stout;
- Plutonium Fuel = "Wizard Ale" Plutonic Ale;
- Uranium-233 = "Spud Essence" U-233 Vodka;
- Uranium-235 = "Jimmy Donald's" U-235 Whiskey;
- Lithium And Tritium Rods = Lithic And Tritic Conserve Jars;
- ZFB Fuel = "Hotboy" ZFB Zirconic Mulled Wine;
- LES Fuel = "Satan's Hangover" Thoroughly-Distilled Schrabidic Rum.

"Wizard Ale" belongs to the short animation "Wizard Beer" by Worthikids. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6XEOl0hw0RY

ZIRNOX and its relating textures belong to HBM's Nuclear Tech Mod, available for 1.7.10 here
https://modrinth.com/mod/ntm

i do not condone the excessive consumption of alcohol or mixing of radioactive material into beverages or food
